{"tid":1973601,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"Make it last HK - 香港得重光（Into the unknown 粵語改詞版）","createTime":"2020-04-15T09:35:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T08:24:45.000Z","uid":307,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bfea28966124724ee5b7a7aff284c30c23edb785","tid":1973601,"uid":307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T09:35:11.000Z","msg":"見到好似無人post<br />\n佢啲歌詞改得好好同埋唱得幾好聽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zHGK6cljbIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzHGK6cljbIc&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=87709096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zHGK6cljbIc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原曲：Into The Unknown<br />\n改詞：Hilda Chang<br />\n主唱+backing vocal: Hilda Chang<br />\n錄音、混音：Jerome Turner<br />\n<br />\n那裏有聲線 喚叫我<br />\n不管一切 吶喊光復<br />\n從前不理世事被圈上了枷鎖<br />\n猶如小鳥折翼墮進洞裏不飛<br />\n<br />\n今可蛻變 全憑住憤怒來喚我<br />\n心想有一天 （好快會）<br />\n願勝利降這地<br />\n<br />\n我的心裏 我所信 為自由號革命<br />\n全力反抗 永不歸去 在正義裏發聲  <br />\n<br />\n縱使歷時多久 用血汗來換取<br />\n同行並肩 如迎來擊敗重來不放棄<br />\n<br />\n遠處有迴響<br />\n再無血流傷<br />\n盼勇氣榮光歸香港<br />\n<br />\n一起堅持<br />\n昏黑之時<br />\n謹守光明<br />\n奮戰到底<br />\n<br />\n未來後我們會抱著慶祝<br />\n信有天 放肆講<br />\n香港得重光<br />\n<br />\n*We don't own the rights to background music in this video<br />\n<br />\nMake It Last FB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/makeitlasthongkong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmakeitlasthongkong%2F&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%2FJo1w%3D&h=ca37c28c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/makeitlasthongkong/</a><br />\nMake It Last IG: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/makeitlast.hk/?hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmakeitlast.hk%2F%3Fhl%3Den&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQEzlOXIvf7DEkQzrkg%